So I wouldn’t called the programming of the server half-assed, I think we just haven’t had anybody with the ambition to finish it come along yet, but I’m not worried; it will come.

item.title: Rsc f2p
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

Everyone who is interested in programming the RSC servers wish to do it properly, and not half cocked as the RS2 servers were done.

Unless WL finished the whole server on his lonesome, he kind of had to release it publically in an unfinished beta, and because of the timing with the Aryan Invasion, many, many, many, many, noobs grabbed the RS2 private server.

So I wouldn’t called the programming of the server half-assed, I think we just haven’t had anybody with the ambition to finish it come along yet, but I’m not worried; it will come.
